{
  "chapter": 37,
  "chapter_summary": "芮玮与林琼菊经大师伯刘忠柱指点，前往药铺求见药王爷（小老头）。药王爷诊断芮玮所中之毒乃其师兄独门毒药，坦言无力解毒，且声称即便能治也绝不施救。林琼菊绝望之下与药王爷冲突，被点穴摔倒。芮玮强忍剧毒奋力抱起林琼菊，一步一步向药铺外走去。此时街头出现一位疯癫的\"失心女\"，四处寻找自己的心，芮玮认出她竟是自己失散多年的妹妹。芮玮跪地恳求药王爷先救妹妹，药王爷认出失心女颈部所中乃\"牛毛天王针\"，立即施展轻功将失心女带回。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "这就是我们的大老板。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "十斤何首乌治不好，那什么能治好我大哥？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你把他带到里面来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你也坐啊！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "我大哥要请……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "姑娘别错会意，小老头可不会瞧病。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "那你怎知十斤何首乌也治不好我大哥的病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "这个嘛，简单得很，你大哥面膛隐隐发黑，这是毒发现象，谁也看得出，何首乌虽然珍贵却不能解毒，这是更简单的道理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "那你请咱们进来做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "我铺内有几名医生就快来了，待会他们来了替你大哥看看，说不定就能配出一方解药来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "我大哥身中巨毒，就请你配一方解药吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "我——我哪成，我对医药一窍不通。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "一窍不通，万窍通，药王爷，你还装什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "谁教你们来的？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "是我们大师伯指点来见老前辈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你们大师伯是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "大师伯姓刘，名讳上忠下柱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "原来是他，过来，过来，让我瞧瞧你毒伤如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "他倒还没忘我，给我找生意上门，把你手伸了来看看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这毒伤不轻啁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这毒我也没法解。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "怎么没法解？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "世上毒药种类繁多，我哪能全部解得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "大师伯称你圣手如来药王爷，说只要找到你，大哥的毒伤一定能治好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "刘大哥，怨我无法救你师侄，谁教他中的是我师兄独门毒药……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "你一定能治我大哥毒伤，你既称药王爷，决不会治不了，你不能推辞，你不能推辞……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "我就是治得了也不能治，你们快快走吧。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "那你是故意不救我大哥啦？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "正是，你向你们大师伯照实说，我对不起他就是，他要绝几十年老交情，我也不能治。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "快走，快走，多问无益，别耽误时间，你大哥尚有三日可活，尽快去想他法救治吧。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "我大哥真的只有三日可活了吗？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "我的判断决不会错，快去想别的法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "三天内还有什么法子可想，大哥死了，我也不想活了，你一掌趁早劈死我吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你不要命吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "还不快走！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "药王爷，你早早打死我，成全了我吧。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，你不能出力！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你找死吗？嫌死得不快吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "快别用力，快别用力，放下她，放下她……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你这样出力走，百步不到必然丧命。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "多谢阁下关照。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_chu_you_ren",
      "speaker_name": "远处有人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "失心女，失心女，快来看失心女……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我虽不能将你毒伤治好，但还可帮你抑止毒气，教它再过一月不发，其间你可去求别救治。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xin_nv",
      "speaker_name": "失心女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的心，我的心，我的心在哪里……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你大师伯是我老友，我不能完全不顾你，快跟我进去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊，牛毛天王针。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_xin_nv",
      "speaker_name": "失心女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的心，我的心，我的心在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "药王爷，我求你一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "药王爷",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不用求我，我一定将你毒伤止住，世上能救你毒伤者，不只我一人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "你别管我，求求你去救那失心女。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "药王爷",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "她是疯子，我救他做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "你不救我，我一点也不怪你，求你看在大师伯的面上，救救那失心女。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "speaker_name": "药王爷",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你如此关心那失心女，她是你什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yao_wang_ye",
      "text": "她是我妹妹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    }
  ],
